scriptExecutionDTO Data Type

The results of running a script under the context of an action. Contains messages that resulted from its execution

Namespace
(Default)
Properties
name data type type namespace min/max occurs description
artifacts_added scriptExecutionPatchDTO element 0/unbounded The artifacts to add to the incident
messages scriptExecutionMessageDTO element 0/unbounded The messages returned from running the script
milestones_added scriptExecutionPatchDTO element 0/unbounded The milestones to add to the incident
note_replies scriptExecutionPatchDTO element 0/unbounded The replies to add to the note
notes_added scriptExecutionPatchDTO element 0/unbounded The notes to add to the incident
objects_patch scriptExecutionPatchDTO element 0/1 The patch to apply to the input objects of the script
rows_added anyType element 0/1 The rows to add to the given data tables
task_notes_added scriptExecutionPatchDTO element 0/unbounded The notes to add to the task
tasks_added scriptExecutionPatchDTO element 0/unbounded The tasks to add to the incident
